{"tid":1974972,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美議員提案向華索償 凍結資產","createTime":"2020-04-16T08:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T13:36:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fcf5132686722d56c44023dcbd1f0ea1d2d12dfd","tid":1974972,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T08:29:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200416/5DOROVGHXOO7QAPV3UTKPRM73M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200416%2F5DOROVGHXOO7QAPV3UTKPRM73M%2F&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=414ae7a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200416%2F5DOROVGHXOO7QAPV3UTKPRM73M%2F&h=e9c068f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200416/5DOROVGHXOO7QAPV3UTKPRM73M/</a><br />\n<br />\n美議員提案向華索償 凍結資產<br />\n<br />\n中國將迎來美國的痛擊，美國共和黨籍參議員霍利（Josh Hawley，圖）周二牽頭提出《COVID-19受害者正義法案》，要求白宮制裁隱瞞疫情的中國官員，並向中國索賠。美媒近日也有爆出多宗內幕，如美聯社昨日（15日）取得的機密文件揭露出中國領導層早於1月14日就知道疫情嚴重性，6日後才由習近平公開談到疫情，中國外交部沒有回應指控。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：發展中國家勢受衝擊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200416/large/1586966984_3f85.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200416%2Flarge%2F1586966984_3f85.gif&h=fdb05909&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n文件揭中共1月初已知嚴重性<br />\n<br />\n美國參議員霍利指出：「有大量證據表明，中共的謊言，欺騙和無能導致COVID-19轉變成全球性大流行&hellip;&hellip;（中共）必須對他們的受害者負責」。此法允許法院凍結中國政府的資產，以便賠償受害者。法案同時要求白宮加以追究中國私下採取的隱瞞疫情舉動，及令李文亮、艾芬等醫護人員噤聲的行為。另一邊廂，美聯社昨日取得的文件則揭露，中國領導層1月14日就暗中研判疫情將會大流行，惟當時仍只通報41宗病例。美聯社引述專家的推算，當時中國至少有超過3,000人染疫。至1月20日晚，中國國家主席習近平才公開談到疫情。隱瞞疫情期間，武漢舉行了萬家宴，數以百萬計民眾也返鄉過年，病毒從此快速散播。<br />\n<br />\n《華盛頓郵報》專欄作家羅金（Josh Rogin）昨日也獨家發文，指美國駐北京使館自2018年1月開始多次派員前往武漢病毒研究所，美方人員以電報向華府強調，研究所有安全、管理弱點，其蝙蝠冠狀病毒研究也充滿危險性，建議給予更多關注與協助。但其中一封電報本為公開的新聞稿，上周卻被美方刪除，耐人尋味。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/《華盛頓郵報》"},{"pid":"bbcf9ba3d237fa77d2082a1aaaa2ade11fbc2800","tid":1974972,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T08:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781ad2ce7e77a17099d24232075a1aca3e612f92","tid":1974972,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T11:13:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec5221bfbb0fbc6f510a6adef8f60cb2c27f4c2","tid":1974972,"uid":2607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T11:15:44.000Z","msg":"又係Josh Hawley<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢幫左香港人好多"},{"pid":"9adb29659a192b417a44e29aec6a60efacaa76b0","tid":1974972,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T13:27:34.000Z","msg":"Xi is responsible<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0739c68b82e12d02f4121aa42a30c6ca37a49fd","tid":1974972,"uid":297045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9adb29659a192b417a44e29aec6a60efacaa76b0","tid":1974972,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T13:27:34.000Z","msg":"Xi is responsible<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T13:36:00.000Z","msg":"侵: Xi is my best friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}